item.description: ﻿﻿﻿Hi, Trailblazers join us for a night of Ice Cream, and walks around Wolfeboro, we will check out the nightlife and enjoy watching the boats and socializing. If anyone has a boat or lives on the lake and would like to take us out for a boat ride let me know! Other than that we will see you there, if you have any questions you can call me at: 603-312-6735 See you there! Peter
